{"tid":390531,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇Econ 人可以幫幫手","createTime":"2017-09-07T06:59:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T10:49:04.000Z","uid":57378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5006db245f4a222efcc9f2cc1ea2ac2d86666b37","tid":390531,"uid":57378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/145809_c822ffb2ba7aced434494da617bf9f7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F145809_c822ffb2ba7aced434494da617bf9f7f.jpg&h=a3394d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔識計6同7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以幫幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf905b1622dc2dc508bcae76c061524a4aac4e1f","tid":390531,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:35:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pWZ4H6z5I6k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpWZ4H6z5I6k&d=kUOmVkoz4SyC5MjAHsnYIi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1d1c5389\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pWZ4H6z5I6k</a><br />\n<br />\n你依條係Cobb-Douglas utility function，如果學過Lagrange multiplier可以試下睇依條片。<br />\n如果無學過的話，你自己set MRS = relative price都會計到"},{"pid":"bc0bae5b55cbf160e2ea3979166f7ab11e47fea6","tid":390531,"uid":57378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pWZ4H6z5I6k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpWZ4H6z5I6k&d=kUOmVkoz4SyC5MjAHsnYIi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1d1c5389\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pWZ4H6z5I6k</a><br />\n<br />\n你依條係Cobb-Douglas utility function，如果學過Lagrange multiplier可以試下睇依條片。<br />\n如果無學過的話，你自己set MRS = relative price都會計到</blockquote><br />\n我計完但係個答案係分數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我想問吓你可唔可以幫我幫我計吓個答案同我唔一樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6876ccd7e3a46b776c84670f8861de76e358c4","tid":390531,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/145809_c822ffb2ba7aced434494da617bf9f7f.jpg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F145809_c822ffb2ba7aced434494da617bf9f7f.jpg%22&d=kUOmVkoz4SyC5MjAHsnYIi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=09147a16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/145809_c822ffb2ba7aced434494da617bf9f7f.jpg&quot;</a>  /&gt;<br />\n唔識計6同7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以幫幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有 Utility function 加埋 budget constraint，要做 optimization 就係 optimize utility subjected to budget constraint. By method of Lagrange multiplier, 你計咗 partial derivative of utility function with respect to x1, x2 ，然後 set = 0 ，換一換 subject，之後再 plug 入 budget constraint constraint 就得。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae70364c79d70afe9b0d61858d6b9171785ba9d8","tid":390531,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:41:39.000Z","msg":"上網都有電腦 program 你可以 check answer. <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wolframalpha.com/widgets/view.jsp?id=1451afdfe5a25b2a316377c1cd488883  \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wolframalpha.com%2Fwidgets%2Fview.jsp%3Fid%3D1451afdfe5a25b2a316377c1cd488883%20%20&d=kUOmVkoz4SyC5MjAHsnYIi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5b250845\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.wolframalpha.com/widgets/view.jsp?id=1451afdfe5a25b2a316377c1cd488883  </a>"},{"pid":"b5351b69aea297683e58d362c475c682684759e3","tid":390531,"uid":57378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T09:55:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/145809_c822ffb2ba7aced434494da617bf9f7f.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F145809_c822ffb2ba7aced434494da617bf9f7f.jpg&d=kUOmVkoz4SyC5MjAHsnYIi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f82756cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/145809_c822ffb2ba7aced434494da617bf9f7f.jpg</a>&quot;  /&gt;<br />\n唔識計6同7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以幫幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有 Utility function 加埋 budget constraint，要做 optimization 就係 optimize utility subjected to budget constraint. By method of Lagrange multiplier, 你計咗 partial derivative of utility function with respect to x1, x2 ，然後 set = 0 ，換一換 subject，之後再 plug 入 budget constraint constraint 就得。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3422657dd7c4004d5387e85f5f545c6c282bb0bd","tid":390531,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:10:19.000Z","msg":"1.Find (du/dx1)/(du/dx2)=p1/p2<br />\n<br />\n2.Sub (1.) into p1x1+p2x2=$600<br />\n<br />\n3.Sub (3.) into (2.) or (1.)<br />\n<br />\n4.Solved<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a738934e6e37149d222be0bf9da19b2bfecdcc74","tid":390531,"uid":57378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T10:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1.Find (du/dx1)/(du/dx2)=p1/p2<br />\n<br />\n2.Sub (1.) into p1x1+p2x2=$600<br />\n<br />\n3.Sub (3.) into (2.) or (1.)<br />\n<br />\n4.Solved<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />